events.text: Hey
hi
How'd you get in here?
the door was unlocked
Hm. I guess I just assumed hotel doors locked themselves
generally a safe assumption
Oh well. I'm GraphicsGale Gareth by the way

i'm microsoft paint michael
what's with all the blenders?
I'm glad you asked

You see. I was attempting to create [rainbow freq=0.2 sat=10 val=20]The Ultimate Protein Shake[/rainbow]
The protein shake to end all protein shakes
A concoction of such [shake rate=5 level=10]tremendous[/shake] power
A nutritional [shake rate=5 level=10]colossus[/shake] of the likes no man had yet to behold
so did you succeed?
Yes
But at a cost
You see
This wasn't just an [wave amp=50 freq=2]ordinary[/wave] protein shake
When I took a sip of my glorious creation I lost all memory of how I made it
Maybe this is fate
Maybe such a protein shake was never meant to exist
And in daring to drink my swole smoothie...
I become too comfortable playing God
How could I have not seen this coming
In my infinite hubris I grew blind to the perils of power
Just as Prometheus stole fire from the gods. So too have I stolen this protein shake
And now I must suffer their wrath
I grew [wave amp=50 freq=2]soft[/wave]
I showed [shake rate=5 level=10]vulnerability[/shake]
I flew too close to the sun
And now God has cast me down
Maybe the nectar of Gods was not meant to be sipped by man
But you know what they say
what do they say?
Science doesn't progress without being an affront to God and a literal abomination of Satan
i don't think people say that

I don't care what people say
I will have my [rainbow freq=0.2 sat=10 val=20]Perfect Protein Shake[/rainbow]
And God can eat my swole, protein flavored ass cheeks
cool
Would you care to join me in unearthing the secrets of humanity's most powerful protein shake?
[wave amp=50 freq=2]well...[/wave] i don't normally make a habit of insulting god
but i suppose i can make an exception this time
Excellent
One of these [color=#00FF00]10 blenders[/color] holds my [rainbow freq=0.2 sat=10 val=20]Perfect Protein Shake[/rainbow]
But I wouldn't go tasting them if I were you
Some of them are [color=#0000FF]poisonous[/color]

I'll need you to find which blender holds [rainbow freq=0.2 sat=10 val=20]The Perfect Protein Shake[/rainbow] and what [color=#FF0000]ingredients[/color] I used to make it
I have some notes here and I also left notes with the others in this hotel due to my previous experience with early onset Alzheimer's
Each protien shake includes exactly three of five [color=#FF0000]ingredients[/color] and no two shakes are exactly alike
The five [color=#FF0000]ingredients[/color] used are:
[color=#FF0000]Protein Powder[/color]
[color=#FF0000]E-Girl Bathwater[/color]
[color=#FF0000]Screams of the Unholy[/color]
[color=#FF0000]Blood of a Virgin[/color]
and [color=#FF0000]Pistachios[/color]
Additionally, each ingredient has a unique, exclusive [color=#0000FF]quality[/color]
The [color=#0000FF]qualities[/color] are as follows:
[color=#0000FF]Acidic[/color]
[color=#0000FF]Alkaline[/color]
[color=#0000FF]Absorbant[/color]
[color=#0000FF]Poison[/color]
and [color=#0000FF]Tasty[/color]
Remember, your goal is to find which [color=#00FF00]blender[/color] holds [rainbow freq=0.2 sat=10 val=20]The Perfect Protein Shake[/rainbow] and what [color=#FF0000]ingredients[/color] were used
There are some notes on the table over there and I left some notes with the others around this hotel
are you going to help at all?
Nope! Early onset Alzheimer's, remember?
are you sure that isn't the reason you forgot the ingredients?

Yes. I'm positive. This is the work of God
God was scared because my protein shake was too powerful so he made me lose my memory, and now I need your help
ok cool
